query:
SELECT g.id as gestor_id, g.nome as gestor_nome, g.userId, u.id as user_id, u.name as user_name, u.email as user_email, u.role
FROM gestores g
LEFT JOIN users u ON g.userId = u.id
WHERE g.nome LIKE '%F치bio%' OR g.nome LIKE '%Fabio%' OR u.name LIKE '%F치bio%' OR u.name LIKE '%Fabio%';
